Package: dluhctheme
Type: Package
Title: Creates a Consistent ggplot Theme for DLUHC Graphs 
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Analysis and Data Direcotrate (DLUHC)
Maintainer: RAP Working Group <jamie.thomas@levellingup.gov.uk>
Description: This package contains a generic theme function for any graph to get into a consistent DLUHC style.
    The package also contains full functions which create graphs based on pre-determined inputs
